@page
@model FAQModel
@{
    ViewData["Title"] = "FAQ";
}

<div class="container mt-4">
    <h1 class="mb-4" style="color: var(--accent-light)">Frequently Asked Questions</h1>
    
    <div class="faq-container">
        <div class="faq-section">
            <h2>How does dark mode work?</h2>
            <p>Dark mode automatically syncs with your system settings. Change your device's display settings to update the application's appearance.</p>
        </div>

        <div class="faq-section">
            <h2>How can I view my reflections?</h2>
            <p>Access your reflections through the "Reflections" tab in the navigation bar. You can view, edit, and manage all your saved reflections there.</p>
        </div>

        <div class="faq-section">
            <h2>How do I manage events in the calendar?</h2>
            <p>Navigate to the "Calendar" tab to manage events. Click any date to add events with titles, times, and descriptions. Click existing events to edit or delete them.</p>
        </div>

        <div class="faq-section">
            <h2>Can I print or export my calendar?</h2>
            <p>Yes - use the "Options" button in the Calendar tab to access print functionality. The printable view can also be saved as a PDF.</p>
        </div>

        <div class="faq-section">
            <h2>What if I forget my login details?</h2>
            <p>Use the "Forgot Password" link on the login page and follow the password reset instructions sent to your registered email.</p>
        </div>
    </div>
</div>